ygData.messageBody:
James Schuldes wrote:
>
> From: James Schuldes <jgs@...>
> [in amongst lots of good advice re my previous question, Sylly wrote:]
> - use a drum - do you have MM drums?

Yes, thanks. Got a set this past weekend. I don't care if they ARE
nerfed; I fly! Had a quite a successful weekend (for me). In addition
to the drums, I got my Mudwater Rune, Fiery Vambraces, Shin Greaves,
Basalt Carapace, and won a lotto for the Ring of the Goblin Lord. Plus,
I got to explore Sol A for the first time, mapped lots of Upper Guk, and
saw some of Lower Guk and parts of Cazic Thule that I had never ventured
into before. Killed all sorts of creatures on my personal hate list
using Chain/Fear (Dorn died three times - I'm still not even), got in my
first Charm kiting practice (I stink at it). Oh, and I got a full level
out of the deal.

Kenross Cantoforjado, 34 songs, Innoruuk
